title: Kin Dza Dza hardcoded English subs.avi
description: KinDzaDza is a sweet Russian SciFi. It's cold, and these two guys notice a man not wearing any shoes, and babbling about how he lost the way home to his galaxy, far away. They say that if he can't find the way, they will take him to a warm place in-doors, where he can sort it out. One of the two guys takes the thing and presses it...and the two are transported to another place, far away. Good SciFi!
